short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Replaces references to the worlds most nonexistent roleplaying game with other RPG's that actually exist.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: There's a certain tabletop roleplaying game that gets talked about a lot. Some might say too much. At least it did, until this extension came along. Variety is the spice of life, so get some spice into your RPG discourse!
